= Concepts =

The Cybersecurity Viewpoint allows the top-down transition of cybersecurity elements (Threats and Primary Assets) and their dependencies. For more details on transitions, check out the [[ ../../../help/topic/org.polarsys.capella.transitions.doc/html/11.%20Iterative%20Transitions/11.1.%20Concepts.html | Capella Documentation]] on the subject.

== Performing a transition ==

Transition of cybersecurity elements can be done using the "Cybersecurity Transition" command available in the transitions menu.


[[Image:../../../Images/cyber%20transition%20pkg.PNG]]

The cybersecurity transition command is available on the following elements:

* On the architecture levels (Operational, System or Logical)

* On the cybersecurity package

* On the cybersecurity elements (Threats and Primary Assets)



